{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be sleek and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Wave Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e52b50; /* A strong red */\n            --secondary-color: #f08080; /* A lighter, softer red */\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background for sleekness */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --hover-color: #ff4500; /* A slightly brighter red for hover effects */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        .content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .content h2 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(229, 43, 80, 0.4);\n            border-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 180px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(229, 43, 80, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--hover-color), var(--primary-color));\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: #aaa;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n\n            .content h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Crimson Wave Network</h1>\n            <p>Hear the stories that matter, amplified.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"content\">\n            <h2>Our Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/e52b50/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+1\" alt=\"Podcast 1 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>The Sonic Chronicle</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the history of sound and its impact on our lives.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/f08080/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+2\" alt=\"Podcast 2 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Insights</h3>\n                    <p>Deep dives into current events with expert analysis and opinion.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/e52b50/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+3\" alt=\"Podcast 3 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>Whispers in the Red</h3>\n                    <p>Unraveling mysteries and true crime stories with a unique perspective.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/f08080/ffffff?text=Podcast+Art+4\" alt=\"Podcast 4 Artwork\">\n                    <h3>The Dialogue Chamber</h3>\n                    <p>Conversations that challenge your thinking and broaden your horizons.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Discover More Podcasts</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"content\" style=\"margin-top: 60px;\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Interested in joining the network or have a suggestion?</p>\n            <p>Email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonwavenetwork.com\">info@crimsonwavenetwork.com</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media for the latest updates.</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Wave Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Designed with passion by the Crimson Wave Team.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll animation for buttons\n        document.querySelectorAll('.cta-button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);\n                const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);\n                if (targetElement) {\n                    targetElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });\n                }\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}